Floyd Mayweather and Manny Pacquiao may only be nine days away from touching gloves but that hasn't stopped them rubbing shoulders with the rich and famous. 

While Pacquiao was making another appearance on Jimmy Kimmel Live, Mayweather was welcoming Mariah Carey to his gym.

Carey has long been a fan of Mayweather having attended his fight against Shane Mosley in 2010.

